{"tid":352553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果喺香港行路要考牌咁幾好呢…","createTime":"2017-08-09T00:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T00:28:39.000Z","uid":129185,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9d0e9b4a6b7c30b062df8ab9e43026b6ca835d","tid":352553,"uid":129185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:28:39.000Z","msg":"(FF) 如果喺香港行路要考牌咁幾好呢&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n1) 右線係快線, 悠閒/廢老/新牌仔要行左線<br />\n2) 唔畀停留喺路中央聚集<br />\n3) 過線爬頭要向後望盲點, 咪撚搞到後面隔離線既炒車<br />\n4) 唔夠位硬攝嗰啲會被處以畀人瘋狂踩腳之刑<br />\n5) 細路(分岔路)出大路要讓大路行先<br />\n6) 唔可以並排行晒幾條線, 阻9住後面<br />\n7) 仲有無其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n違者會畀扣分, 扣晒啲分之後會禁足三五七日不等。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}